{"tid":1382240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 而家流傳緊嘅水泡照係由接觸性皮炎造成","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:55:25.000Z","uid":86943,"like":138,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf50a7012362821f2994f12f4038acc83ba8b33","tid":1382240,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:12:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家唔好再誤傳係chemical burn，兩者相差好大</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n接觸性皮炎喺由irritant，如化學物質(以今次嘅例子係CS gas為主，由CS multi gas發出) 持續接觸造成嘅皮膚急性敏感，以圖片嚟睇屬於極度嚴重，有機會係<br />\n<br />\nA:當事人無洗走所有tear gas，殘留物導致接觸性皮炎<br />\n類似例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QP31f4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQP31f4A.jpg&h=2670fef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nB:當事人皮膚易敏感，係當晚接觸太多tear gas造成該症狀<br />\n<br />\nFact: <br />\n接觸性皮炎<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contact_dermatitis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FContact_dermatitis&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ea30c20c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contact_dermatitis</a><br />\n(註:可以上google搵到嚴重接觸性皮炎嘅照片)<br />\n<br />\nCS gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/CS_gas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCS_gas&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=7ba5c632\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/CS_gas</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;對CS的防護，不但要用防毒面具進行臉部及眼和呼吸道的防護，而且有時還需穿防護衣及靴套、手套等，對皮膚進行防護，中毒者可用2%碳酸氫鈉水溶液或清水沖洗眼、鼻和皮膚。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係未來要清洗CS gas 嘅 時候建議用2%蘇打粉溶液，同埋絕對要徹底洗凈<br />\n<br />\n呢部分close file，有待當事人出現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後講幾句聽到悶嘅<br />\n<br />\n唔好隨便謠傳信息，要fact check，避免散播恐慌<br />\n<br />\n追究警方使用過期裝備，令市民生命進一步收到危險"},{"pid":"02a6e4eda50bfab74c452128981b331fb766c5ad","tid":1382240,"uid":86943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a7eebe66fcae723ba2255b41cc34df4d2c28464","tid":1382240,"uid":278285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97236a2b4eb6030256cc4f2796146475121ea7b7","tid":1382240,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7526d30335802e81403a116a1a715bc8a6e10175","tid":1382240,"uid":81183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"咁其實都係關tear gas事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都可以鬧黑狗架"},{"pid":"7fbb3669765711a0cbaecc3cb55bb1ff258d3f6a","tid":1382240,"uid":150761,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"‪當事人打左消炎針 出左消炎藥同藥膏 並包紥好‬<br />\n‪因為當時人冇做防護下衝左去滅火 所以導致化學灼傷‬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">‪所以防護好重要！！‬</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申 認識當事人"},{"pid":"f103439d4bccf49039d709b74f098acb3e109b36","tid":1382240,"uid":86943,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"7526d30335802e81403a116a1a715bc8a6e10175","tid":1382240,"uid":81183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"咁其實都係關tear gas事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都可以鬧黑狗架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"當然啦，絕對關tear gas事，要追究嘅包括：<br />\n<br />\n過度使用tear gas<br />\n使用過期裝備<br />\n以不恰當方式使用防暴裝備，導致危害公眾安全<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好放錯焦點俾佢有下台階"},{"pid":"b32c9445007fcf32f9dae6ad5f6619d24b91196b","tid":1382240,"uid":130901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7526d30335802e81403a116a1a715bc8a6e10175","tid":1382240,"uid":81183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"咁其實都係關tear gas事<img src=\"/assets/faces/no